OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA pleasant
OL,6,Fevening with plenty of sunny spells
OL,7,Flate in the day. Winds will gradually
OL,8,Fease, becoming light for most. A
OL,9,Fmostly clear night will follow,
OL,10,Fbecoming cool in rural locations.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FVariable cloud on Friday, but
OL,13,Fplenty of sunny spells through the
OL,14,Fday. Warm to very warm in the
OL,15,Fsunshine. Light winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
